'''Duchess''' was a title of [[Noble|nobility]]. During the reign of the pacifist [[New Mandalorians|New Mandalorian]] government, [[Satine Kryze]] ruled as the Duchess of the [[planet]] [[Mandalore]].<ref name="The Mandalore Plot" /> The [[Arc Pulse Generator]] was later nicknamed "the Duchess" after her.<ref name="Heroes of Mandalore">''[[Star Wars Rebels: Heroes of Mandalore]]''</ref> [[Celly Organa]] was a duchess of [[House of Organa]] of the [[Elder Houses]].<ref name="Part I" />

